org.hibernate.ogm.loader.nativeloader.impl

Class BackendCustomQuery<T extends Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.loader.nativeloader.impl.BackendCustomQuery<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, CustomQuery

    public class BackendCustomQuery<T extends Serializable>
extends Object
implements CustomQuery, Serializable
    Extension point allowing any NoSQL native query with named and positional parameters to be executed by OGM on the corresponding backend, returning managed entities, collections and simple scalar values.
    Author:
    Davide D'Alto <davide@hibernate.org>
